{"_path":"/maps/_ai/agents","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"智能体 (AI Agents)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"智能体-ai-agents"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"智能体 (AI Agents)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"langchain构建-llm-应用的编排框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain：构建 LLM 应用的编排框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain 提供构建 LLM 应用的标准组件：Chains（将多个 LLM 调用串联成工作流）、Agents（动态决策调用哪些工具）、Memory（对话历史管理）、Callbacks（日志、监控集成）。支持 ReAct（推理+行动交替）、Plan-and-Execute（先制定计划再执行）、Structured Chat（结构化输出解析）等 Agent 类型。是构建复杂 LLM 应用的首选框架。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://langchain.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.langchain.com/react-agent-benchmarking/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ReAct Agent 基准测试"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gi7nqB37WEY","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain Agents 教程"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"llamaindex数据增强的-agent-开发框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex：数据增强的 Agent 开发框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex 专注于\"数据增强的 Agent\"——连接 LLM 与私有数据。提供 100+ Data Connectors（PDF、SQL、API 等数据源）、多种 Index Types（向量索引、树索引、图索引）、Query Engines（RAG、多文档问答）。Workflow 机制允许定义复杂的 Agent 协作流程，结合工具调用与检索能力，是 RAG 和知识库应用的首选。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.llamaindex.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/framework/understanding/rag/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LlamaIndex RAG 指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.llamaindex.ai/blog/automate-workflows-with-document-agents-a-complete-tutorial-to-building-context-aware-AI","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Document Agents 工作流"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"crewai多-agent-协作框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI：多 Agent 协作框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 将 Agent 定义为具有角色、目标和工具的\"数字员工\"，通过定义任务依赖实现协作。支持 Role-Playing Agents（专业化角色设定）、Autonomous Collaboration（自主协作）、Task Delegation（任务委托）。适合研究报告生成、代码审查流水线、客户服务自动化等需要多角色协作的场景。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.crewai.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.crewai.com/en/introduction","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/crewai-crash-course-role-based-agent-orchestration","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CrewAI 实战指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"autogpt自主-agent-先驱"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AutoGPT：自主 Agent 先驱"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AutoGPT 是首个引发广泛关注的自主 Agent 项目，展示了 LLM 独立完成任务的可能性：目标分解将大目标拆分为可执行步骤、自主循环（观察-思考-行动-记忆）、工具使用（文件操作、网络搜索、代码执行）。但也面临循环陷阱、成本失控、可靠性等现实挑战，更多用于探索性任务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/Significant-Gravitas/AutoGPT","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AutoGPT GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"agent-的记忆问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent 的记忆问题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"ai-记忆层次的缺陷"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 记忆层次的缺陷"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人类记忆层次包括感觉记忆、短期记忆和长期记忆，可随时将短期记忆巩固为长期记忆。但 AI 系统仅有两种记忆：上下文作为短期记忆（任务结束即清除）、模型权重作为长期记忆（需昂贵训练才能更新）。这种缺失限制了 Agent 的持续学习和个性化能力。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"为什么记忆对-agent-至关重要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么记忆对 Agent 至关重要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"想象一下：如果软件工程师每天醒来后对公司代码库一无所知，又要重新开始入职培训；如果每次与朋友聊天都忘记之前的对话内容。这正是当前 AI Agent 的处境——缺乏将短期经验转化为长期记忆的灵活机制。ChatGPT 的\"记忆功能\"尝试通过提取用户偏好摘要来解决这一问题，但仍显初级。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"持续学习评估的缺失"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续学习评估的缺失"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"学术界面临的核心挑战不是缺少方法，而是缺少合适的评估基准。当研究者尝试让 Agent 从过往任务中学习时，审稿人往往质疑\"这对其他方法不公平\"。这种评估困境阻碍了持续学习 Agent 的发展。真正的突破需要重新设计评估设定，从评估\"现有能力\"转向评估\"学习能力\"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ysymyth.github.io/The-Second-Half/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Second Half - 长期记忆"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"框架选择指南"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"框架选择指南"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain 适合复杂 LLM 应用，学习曲线中等；LlamaIndex 适合 RAG 和知识库，学习曲线平缓；CrewAI 适合多角色协作场景，学习曲线平缓；AutoGPT 适合探索性任务，学习曲线陡峭。实际项目中常组合使用，如 LlamaIndex 负责数据检索，LangChain 负责工具编排，CrewAI 负责多 Agent 协作。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://damodev.csdn.net/69671cabea53844658f6afed.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 主流 AI Agent 框架调研"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://draftnrun.com/en/blog/250915-ai-agent-frameworks-comparison/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangChain vs LlamaIndex vs CrewAI 对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"多-agent-架构模式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多 Agent 架构模式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"通用智能体-业务领域-agent"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通用智能体 + 业务领域 Agent"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一种适用于企业级多业务系统的分层架构模式："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"角色划分："}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通用主 Agent"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：负责意图识别、对话管理、任务分发"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"业务领域 Agent"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：专注特定业务领域（如订单、库存、客服）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"后端服务"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：通过 OpenAPI 提供业务逻辑，经 FunctionAI Toolset 接入"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"优势："}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"业务解耦"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：各业务线独立开发部署自己的 Agent"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"协议标准化"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：通过 A2A 等协议实现跨系统协作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低摩擦集成"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：现有 REST API 可快速转化为 Agent 工具"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"典型案例："}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/agents/a2a"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希希咖啡店"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 基于 Google ADK + A2A 协议的咖啡点单与配送协同"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"agent-协议选择"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent 协议选择"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"协议"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"适用场景"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代表案例"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A2A"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent 与 Agent 之间的协作"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希希咖啡店的多 Agent 协同"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A2UI"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent 驱动 UI 界面渲染"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"声明式 UI 协议"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agent 与工具/资源的连接"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Claude Desktop 的工具调用"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/agents/a2a"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A2A 协议详解"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modelcontextprotocol.io/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MCP 规范"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"langchain构建-llm-应用的编排框架","depth":2,"text":"LangChain：构建 LLM 应用的编排框架"},{"id":"llamaindex数据增强的-agent-开发框架","depth":2,"text":"LlamaIndex：数据增强的 Agent 开发框架"},{"id":"crewai多-agent-协作框架","depth":2,"text":"CrewAI：多 Agent 协作框架"},{"id":"autogpt自主-agent-先驱","depth":2,"text":"AutoGPT：自主 Agent 先驱"},{"id":"agent-的记忆问题","depth":2,"text":"Agent 的记忆问题"},{"id":"框架选择指南","depth":2,"text":"框架选择指南"},{"id":"多-agent-架构模式","depth":2,"text":"多 Agent 架构模式"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:agents.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/agents.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/agents","_extension":"md"}